This can be acquired at present by nearly 100,000 people who own the Opencard chip card.
Passengers can buy the 30-day, 90-day and annual bonus (this will be valid from 1 January 2009) and simultaneously charge it on their chip card at the infocentres and posts of the transport company at the stations of the Metro, Muzeum, Mŭstek, Nádraží Holešovice, Anděl, Roztyly, Letňany, Kobylisy, Rajská zahrada, Kačerov and Luka.
