\"In the stamp the name of our company and the NIF appeared in the wrong place\"
He added: in addition to formal problems, he did not agree that a hundred people were housed according to the invoice, since they have only eleven rooms in which so many people do not fit.
In addition, meals were also included on the invoice, while the restaurant has not worked for a long time.
The enthusiastic invoice manufacturers were also not informed that the travel agency elected in Budapest exclusively organises trips abroad, so that in the cash bill they foolishly indicated as a service a trip within Hungary, which did not coincide with the agency's billing practice.
